name: Stranger Smoking
description: As a part of our imagination, we have dreams at night. And when we are awake sometimes we see strange objects appearing infront of our eyes, like parts of those dreams. "Stranger Smoking" is a person from my dream, who appeared on my balkony once. Human brain works initially within our memories, so the shapes depicted are partly real ones. That's what we call daydreaming. And this peace of mine is a digital dream.
